            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Additional notes\r\n\r\n### Showcase\r\nBefore: NVIM v0.11.5\r\nAfter: build from this PR\r\n\r\n<img width=\"2500\" height=\"1600\" alt=\"demo\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/4a4fc5c9-6c7f-45a2-b22e-de732f6b286c\" />\r\n\r\n### TODO\r\n- [ ] `colorcolumn` looks/behaves inconsistent with `wrapcolumn` \r\n- [ ] Add functional tests\r\n- [ ] Add option value validation (reject negative values)\r\n- [ ] Verify/update documentation\r\n",
